Package: quanteda.extras
Title: Additional Corpus Functions for Quanteda
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Brown",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dwb2@andrew.cmu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7745-6354"))
Description: Provides additional statistical and plotting tools that expand 
    the functionality of quanteda. Includes functions for calculating keyness, 
    effect sizes, dispersion measures, and collocations. These tools are 
    useful for corpus linguistics and text analysis research.
